  "title": "Collecting groundnut germplasm in Tanzania",
  "abstract": "During a collecting mission in April-May, 1985, 96 samples were collected: most matured in c. 120 days. Details are given of provenance. The local names of 8 varieties are listed by region, together with their salient features",
